1 THAT CompSource Mutual Insurance Company is hereby prohibited
2 from pursuing any means to change its corporate structure from the
3 mutual insurance company previously allowed by the Legislature
4 except for the change to a mutual insurance holding company.
5
6 DIRECT TO CALENDAR.
